<h2 class="content-heading">About Jump Box</h2>
<div style="float:left;width:460px;margin-right:30px;">
  <p><strong>Jump Box</strong> is a premium Ajax based CV(Resume)/Portfolio animated website template. This template is perfect to use for small websites. It can be used as a CV/Portfolio Template, Landing Page, or any website with a little number of pages. All additional content pages/articles could be loaded into the popup window.</p>
  <p>The main advantage of this template is that it uses only one page. Content pages slides across the screen. This site and all its pages are loading at the same time, no need to wait until the user will load the desired page. If you want to use the extra content, you can use the Ajax features (popup window) of this template. &quot;Slide Engine&quot; of this template allows you to make absolutely dufferent design for every page (slide).</p>
  <p><strong>Jump Box</strong> is ready to use with with a four pages: Home (About), Resume, Portfolio, Contacs (Ajax contact form with validation). Template comes with amazing animation. Smooth and good looking animation and Ajax features of this template are realized with the JavaScript jQuery library and CSS3.</p>
  <p><strong>Rotate animation will work in latest versions of major browsers: Firefox 4+, Chrome 9+, Safari 4+, Opera 10.6+</strong></p>
  <p><strong>Jump Box is provided with 17 layered PSD files (4 pages X 4 color themes + Ajax loader) and full illustrated PDF documentation.</strong></p>
</div>
